From Segwaying, sailing and shopping, to live music, nightlife and a buzzing food scene, Stuart really is the heartbeat of Martin County, Florida.

Around two hours north of Miami is the characterful city of Stuart in Martin County. With colourful buildings that look like something out of a movie, great restaurants and a magical location on the St Lucie River, it’s easy to see why Stuart was named America’s Happiest Seaside Town
